 has a level 46 warrior, I was curious what I need to do to get him better geared and leveled up.<br>
<br>
1. Where is the best place for him to get a group and level at 46?<br>
<br>
2. What armor should he be getting at this level, should he start trying to go to PoH and get some of that gear?He has some cobalt armor and some Crusty crap. If he can't go to PoH what should he save up for and buy?<br>
<br>
3. What weapons should he get. He currently has a Venomous Axe of the Velium Brood (sp) and a long sword of some crap.<br>
<br>
Thank you all very much.<br>
<br>
