<br>
Can't really help with gear without a magelo profile, otherwise it's just guesswork.  Though for weapons, ditch the longsword, and put a Frostbringer in main.  But I don't know how much you have to spend, so I can't be sure you can afford it.  If you can't, a black blade of tormenting is good aggro, though its ratio is fairly weak.  Praetor's blade of debility is nice too, and quested so it's free. <p>Veteran Overdorf <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=18306">Hussar</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> Kneeslicer - <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub189.ezboard.com/bdrunkentsunami">Drunken Tsunami</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=thornyeq>ThornyEQ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 40<br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/14/03 11:01:39 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5490.topic&index=2>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_exp.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Question on it all, exp, weap, armor</span><hr size=1> Weeeeell...if you and your friend duo, or if he spends his time mostly in KC/DL exp groups, and the &quot;long sword of crap&quot; is actually a long sword of ethereal energy (lotta if's, huh?), then keep it and use it off-hand. You won't find a better off-hander for a good long while if DPS is more important than aggro at those levels.<br>
